episodes.description:
Join us for a special livestream celebration as we hit *500 subscribers*! 🎉 On *October 17th at 4pm Central*, we'll be going live to chat with all of you, reflect on our journey, and discuss where the channel is heading next. We're excited to have some fantastic content creators joining us, so pop in, join the live chat, and be part of the conversation!

We've invited some of the atheist content creator friends we've made along the way, and the confirmed attendees are: 
@AronRa
@GodlessEngineer
@HarmonicAtheist
Author David Fitzgerald
@BetterThanEmber
@TheKentuckyAtheist

Some of our other favorite content creators on YouTube are: 
@GodlessGranny
@DaranteLaMar
@misterdiffiCULT1
@PunkApostate
@theStaciesMomPodcast
@NeilThe604Atheist
@AmbushedApostate
...and many more......

For those new to the channel, *Apostate Sisters* is all about deconstructing faith, unpacking life in high-control religious environments like the Worldwide Church of God, and creating healing spaces for those on their own journeys. We tackle topics like religious trauma, bodily autonomy, and reclaiming agency, all while building a supportive community.

Mark your calendars and come celebrate with us! We couldn't have reached this milestone without you.
